               <p>and the reason he took the sovereign, he said, was that he wanted a pair of shoes, and he had 30<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. coming to him from his mistress—when I accused him of it, he abused me shamefully, and said he would have me taken up for accusing him falsely.</p>
